
The Slackers.it Repository 

======================================================================

instant-markdown-d (Instant Markdown previews from VIm)

instant-markdown-d is a small Node.js server that enables instant
compilation and previewing of Markup files. A plugin can easily be
written for any text editor to interface with it. 

HOME: https://github.com/suan/instant-markdown

======================================================================
REQUIRES: node npm

